headline: Uber's ALDI Deal on Grocery Delivery: Growth Thesis Strengthening?
summary: UBER's partnership with ALDI brings fresh groceries, SNAP payments and exclusive deals to Uber Eats, boosting its growing delivery segment.

headline: ALDI Joins Uber Eats to Offer On-Demand Grocery Delivery Coast to Coast
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, September 25, 2025--Today, Uber Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: UBER) and ALDI, America’s fastest-growing grocer, announced a new collaboration to bring its award-winning ALDI selection of organic meats, fresh produce, gourmet cheeses, globally-sourced wine, bread and bakery treats, seasonal items and so much more, to Uber Eats.
